  <brief_title>Radiofrequency Ablation Plus Botulinum Toxin Injection Versus Radiofrequency Ablation Only in Patients With Atrial Flutter</brief_title>
  <official_title>Radiofrequency Ablation Plus Botulinum Toxin Injection Versus Radiofrequency Ablation Only in Patients With Atrial Flutter to Prevent Post-procedural Atrial Fibrillation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
